data.description: Fall in Love with this beautiful 5 bedroom 3 full bath home! Located in the Heart of the City of Calhoun! You will love taking refreshing walks to downtown and around Historic College street.  This adorable home comes with a newly stained rear deck and a Privacy fence perfect to enjoy those summer time cookouts! With a Newly installed roof and A/C units, You will love the hardwood floors throughout the home! Upstairs features a lovely Tile shower to go along with a beautiful bathtub. The high ceilings in the Master bedroom gives you that spacious feeling you want! An explendid Bonus room with its very own bathroom is perfect for a guest! This fantastic home could be used as an In- Law suite as well, Giving you the comfort and ease of mind for your loved one. A Cellar with so much potential is located under the home. Previously used as a Wine Cellar. You could turn this into your very own man cave, Storage room, or what ever your heart and mind desires! Located in the Calhoun City School District, it is only a 5 minute drive to School as well as I75. Are you ready for the next chapter in your life? Make it a memorable one!
